    </step>
    <step order="1" name="Load context">
      Read project CLAUDE.md + spec.md FR-16 + plan.md Wave 3 + task 030 design doc + existing AI-ARCHITECTURE.md.
    </step>
    <step order="2" name="Find best placement in AI-ARCHITECTURE.md">
